            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Transfer the cheesy pasta mix </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, then top with the<strong> smoky breadcrumbs</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 20-25 min or until it's golden – this is your <strong>smoky bacon, mushroom & leek mac 'n' cheese</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, trim, then chop your <strong>green beans </strong>in half,  then add to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p>",
